trans-unit.source: Implements a set of predefined <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.SolidColorBrush" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Implementa um conjunto de objetos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.SolidColorBrush" /> predefinidos.

trans-unit.source: Color names in Windows Presentation Foundation match the color names in the .NET Framework, Windows Forms, and [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Nomes de cor no Windows Presentation Foundation correspondem aos nomes de cor no .NET Framework, o Windows Forms e [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: These colors and their names are based on the UNIX X11 color values.
trans-unit.target: Essas cores e seus nomes são baseados no UNIX X11 valores de cor.

trans-unit.source: The following image shows the color of each predefined brush, its name, and its hexadecimal value.
trans-unit.target: A imagem a seguir mostra a cor de cada pincel predefinido, seu nome e seu valor hexadecimal.

trans-unit.source: ![Predefined colors](~/add/media/art-color-table.png "Predefined colors")
trans-unit.target: ![Predefinido de cores](~/add/media/art-color-table.png "predefinido de cores")

trans-unit.source: Color table including a color swatch, the color name, and the hexadecimal value
trans-unit.target: Tabela de cores, incluindo uma amostra de cor, o nome da cor e o valor hexadecimal

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Brush> class for a variety of other, more complex, ways that you can paint an area.
trans-unit.target: Consulte o <xref:System.Windows.Media.Brush> classe para uma variedade de maneiras de outros, mais complexas, que você pode pintar uma área.

trans-unit.source: For example, try using gradients (<xref:System.Windows.Media.LinearGradientBrush>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.RadialGradientBrush>) or images (<xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageBrush>).
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, tente usar gradientes (<xref:System.Windows.Media.LinearGradientBrush>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.RadialGradientBrush>) ou imagens (<xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageBrush>).

trans-unit.source: Gets the solid fill color that has a hexadecimal value of <c>#FFF0F8FF</c>.

trans-unit.source: A frozen <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.SolidColorBrush" /> with a <see cref="P:System.Windows.Media.SolidColorBrush.Color" /> of <c>#FFF0F8FF</c>.
trans-unit.target: Um congelada <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.SolidColorBrush" /> com um <see cref="P:System.Windows.Media.SolidColorBrush.Color" /> de <c>FFF0F8FF #</c>.

trans-unit.source: Because the brush returned by this property is frozen (its <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen%2A> property is **true**), it can't be animated.
trans-unit.target: Porque o pincel retornado por essa propriedade está congelado (seu <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen%2A> é de propriedade **true**), ela não pode ser animada.

trans-unit.source: For information about how to animate a SolidColorBrush, see [How to: Animate the Color or Opacity of a SolidColorBrush](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-animate-the-color-or-opacity-of-a-solidcolorbrush.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter informações sobre como animar um SolidColorBrush, consulte [como: animar a cor e a opacidade de um SolidColorBrush](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-animate-the-color-or-opacity-of-a-solidcolorbrush.md).
